<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-87-0100 </DOCNO><TEXT>In 1953 Slater proposed a linearized version of the APW method based onthe augmented basis functions with continuous function values and firstderivatives at the muffin-tin radius. A modification is described ofthis method and a numerical scheme which makes it suitable for practicalband structure calculations. As an example, the energy structure of Cuis evaluated. (author). 2 figs., 2 tabs., 11 refs.</TEXT></DOC>